http://localhost:3000/api/reminders/set (post)
{
  "mealType": "lunch",
  "time": "13:00"
}
output:
{
    "message": "Reminder set",
    "reminder": {
        "user": "685971ed5fd982c78f27a01d", <-- User ID
        "mealType": "lunch",
        "time": "13:00",
        "active": true,
        "_id": "685fc2ac5cf08a98b82efe73",<-- Reminder Document ID
        "__v": 0
    }
}
Get active reminder: 
http://localhost:3000/api/reminders/get (get)

Deactivate a Reminder
http://localhost:3000/api/reminders/deactivate (PATCH)
{
  "mealType": "lunch"
}
